    <item>
      <title>Pi Pico 2W with Waveshare Pico ePaper 2.13</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/pico-epaper-2.13/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/pico-epaper-2.13/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I recently picked up a Pico-ePaper-2.13 from Waveshare. This is a great, small e-ink display with a fast refresh time designed for interfacing with the Pi Pico. I want to make a few things with this, but I&amp;rsquo;m going to start out making a clock/weather widget display for your desk. I&amp;rsquo;m using a Pi Pico 2W for the extra ooomph, altho a Pi Pico 1W would work for this application.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
